(1, 'Wireless Headphones', 'Premium noise-cancelling over-ear headphones with 40-hour battery life, deep bass, and ultra-comfortable memory foam cushions. Features Bluetooth 5.3.', 300, 50, 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1505740420928-5e560c06d30e?w=600&q=80'),
